title: New bands- Pack 1
description:
Torrent Info::::


These are songs from 2 bands that I recently discovered.

I&#039;ve been lookin for NEW bands that sound alot like; Motley Crue, and/or Iron Maiden, and/or Megadeth,
and/or etc....

I don&#039;t know if these 2 bands are new, and I don&#039;t know if they do meet the standards of the other bands 
that I stated, but I like em, and I think they come close, I can&#039;t tell because I jsut like them.

Anyways the 2 bands are Black Tide, and Mustasch.

Heres the songs that you should listen to first (hopefully in the order I list them)

From Black Tide:

Black Abyss
Live Fast, Die Young
Warriors of time
Let Me

and the rest are good, I think, I just haven&#039;t had a chance to here every second of All the songs. 



From Mustasch:

Parasite
Down In Black
Bring Me Everyone
Black City
Double Nature (Has some synth that sounds a bit overdone at first, until you really know the song)
Muddy Waters

Same thing, the rest are good, I think, I just haven&#039;t had a chance to here every second of All the songs.



and then 2 random songs from 2 other bands... just because, lol. 

Hope you like these bands, I like discovering new music, and spreading it is pretty cool too 
(at least I think its new, and yes, I consider bands that formed in year 2000 new, at least for this 
type of music)
